    "tactics": "",
    "attacksNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Wind Blade [Combat]:</strong> Melee attack (Agi 7 + Melee Combat 5), Reach: 10 ft\n<ul>\n<li><em>Margin 1:</em> 6 damage; target pushed 10 feet</li>\n<li><em>Margin 2:</em> 9 damage (6 + 3 Str); target pushed 10 feet and knocked Prone; no save</li>\n<li><em>Margin 3:</em> 9 damage + Prone + Stunned until end of their next turn from a concentrated wind impact</li>\n</ul></li>\n<li><strong>Lightning Arc [Combat]:</strong> Ranged attack (Dex 5 + Ranged Combat 4), Range: 60 ft\n<ul>\n<li><em>Margin 1:</em> 8 lightning damage (Half DR)</li>\n<li><em>Margin 2:</em> 13 lightning damage (8 + 5 Dex); target gains Dazed condition until end of their next turn</li>\n<li><em>Margin 3:</em> 13 lightning damage + Dazed + Stunned until end of their next turn</li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul>",
    "specialAbilitiesNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Momentum Defense:</strong> As above.</li>\n<li><strong>Storm Body:</strong> Grapple attempts add 1 to both dice. If successfully grappled, the Stormcall makes a Fortitude save at the start of its turn (1 success) to break free automatically.</li>\n</ul>",
